  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ACCESS TO QUALITY EDUCATION WITH FOCUS ON KARAMOJA IMPROVE QUALITYOF PRIMARY EDUCATION &amp; COORDINATION</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Irelands investment in the education sector is focused on improving access and completion of quality education and training in marginalised areas, with a focus on Karamoja. We work with a range of partners including UNICEF, the Ministry of Education and Sport, and local organisations to address barriers to education, reform vocational education, support skills development and to provide school meals.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Outcome 3: Better access and completion of quality Education and Training in marginalised areas, that increases the resilience of Karmajong children and youth</narrative>
  </description>
